examples.en: She was wearing a loose dress.
The nails had been pried loose.
The rope was tied in a loose knot.
examples.ru: Верёвка была завязана в слабый узел.

examples.en: The soldiers loosed a volley of rifle fire.
Some of the shingles on the roof were loose.
examples.ru: Часть черепицы на крыше была расшатана.

examples.en: The archers loosed a great volley of arrows at the foot soldiers charging towards them.
examples.ru: Лучники осыпали атакующих их пехотинцев огромным градом стрел.
